import React from 'react'
import './custom-button.style.scss'

const CustomButton = ({
    children,
    isGoogleSignIn, 
    inverted, ...otherProps}) => (
    <button className={`${isGoogleSignIn ? 'google-sign-in' : ''} custom-button`} {...otherProps}>
        {children}
    </button>
)

export default CustomButton
